<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Organ Donation Prerequisites | LifeNest</title>

  <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
  <link
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    rel="stylesheet"
  >

  <!-- Glyphicons (from Bootstrap 3 for icons) -->
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
  />

  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8f9fa, #dbeafe);
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .card {
      border: none;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      background-color: white;
      padding: 2rem;
      transition: 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.02);
    }

    .title {
      text-align: center;
      color: #1e40af;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    li {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    li .glyphicon {
      color: #0d6efd;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }

    a.back-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 20px;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      background-color: #1e40af;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    a.back-link:hover {
      background-color: #0d6efd;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="container py-5">
    <div class="card mx-auto" style="max-width: 700px;">
      <h2 class="title"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart"></span> Organ Donation Prerequisites</h2>
      <p class="text-muted text-center mb-4">
        To become an organ donor, please ensure the following requirements are met:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span> Must be at least <strong>20 years old</strong>.</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-ok-circle"></span> Should be medically fit and free from infectious diseases.</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-credit-card"></span> Must have valid ID proof (Aadhaar, PAN, or Driving License).</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></span> Must voluntarily sign an organ donor consent form.</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-home"></span> Family should be informed and supportive of your decision.</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-certificate"></span> Brain death must be certified by authorized doctors.</li>
        <li><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-globe"></span> Donor registration should be done at an authorized center or online.</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-arrow-left"></span> Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
